(76174, 171631, 6894, 4, 'Like Yesterday', '', '2014-05-31 00:00:00', 2014, 19, 2, 9, 'Like Yesterday\n\nYou ask me why\nBut I don''t know how, we can''t reach one another\nWhy we gone so far\nWe were too young to give the words\nBut we both waited\nWhy we stop waiting?\n\nAnd I Still here\nNights remind again how we were\nIt''s just like yesterday\nBut I have no time to get it back again\n\nYou tell me why\nI still don''t know how\nIt seems we have nothing\nnow between us\nYou wipe the tears\nAnd smile to say, one day we''ll go through this\nThis we had before\n\nAnd I Still here\nNights remind again how we were\nIt''s just like yesterday\nBut I have no time to get it back again\nI wanna get it back again\nI wanna get you back to me\n\nI try to make it back to the start when we met\nI try to make a change to the right way\nI wanna get you back to me\n', '', 211, '', '', '', '', 'One Way Street', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-05-23 12:21:21', '2015-03-12 14:07:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
